I'm sorry this seems to be commonplace there. The best thing you can do to bring about change imo, is to begin reporting things that you see. Even if the adults don't listen to you, keep reporting it. If you are in a room where this is happening, do wv u can to get the males to stop and speak up on behalf of the female. Then go tell the school authorities. I trust it is safe for you to do so. If it is not then please find a way to report it anonymously. Also, again if u r able to, speak openly to your friends about how you feel. Spread your thoughts around. The more people who report and change their attitudes the better it will become.
